    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines the rules for encoding IPP operations and IPP attributes into a new Internet mime media type called "application/ipp".  This document also defines the rules for transporting over HTTP a message body whose Content-Type is "application/ipp".  This document defines an Experimental protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
